%%{init: { 'theme': 'default' } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UA as User A Browser
    participant UB as User B Browser
    participant UC as User C Browser (inne gospodarstwo)
    participant SO as Flask-SocketIO Server
    participant RM as RoutesManager
    participant DB as MultiHomeDBManager
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    UA->>UA: kliknij "Toggle Light" (room.html)
    UA->>SO: emit 'toggle_device' {device_id, home_id}
    SO->>RM: wywołaj handler 'toggle_device'
    RM->>RM: waliduj session['user_id'] i session['current_home_id']
    RM->>DB: MultiHomeDBManager.toggle_device(home_id, device_id, user_id)
    DB->>PG: UPDATE devices SET state = NOT state WHERE id = ... AND home_id = ...
    PG-->>DB: zwróć zaktualizowany wiersz
    DB-->>RM: device_data
    RM->>UA: emit 'device_updated' (do użytkownika A)
    UA-->>UA: update UI lokalnie
    RM->>RM: CacheManager.invalidate_cache(f"home:{home_id}:devices")
    RM->>RM: wywołaj _broadcast_device_update(home_id, device_data)
    note right of RM: Iteracja przez użytkowników gospodarstwa
    RM->>SO: emit 'device_updated' do sesji User B (room=session_id)
    SO-->>UB: 'device_updated' (User B otrzymuje update)
    UB-->>UB: update UI
    note over UC: User C należy do innego gospodarstwa
    UC--xSO: (nie otrzymuje 'device_updated')
    note right of RM: Nie używamy broadcast=True — izolacja gospodarstw zachowana

    %% End of sequence
